flowchart TD
  START([matrix_task_start]) --> REG[WDT · matrix_reset · pattern]
  REG --> LOOP{{for ;;}}

  LOOP --> WDT[WDT reset]
  WDT --> CMD[matrix_process_commands — drain matrix_command_queue]
  CMD --> NOTE[Sken GPIO řídí timer callback — ne přímo zde]
  NOTE --> DLY[vTaskDelayUntil 10 ms]
  DLY --> LOOP
